ts tail a white feather,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"feathers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having a whiteness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a colour differing"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the rest"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its hinder part:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and (some say, O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAbirap","text_ar":"دَابِرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA, in the CK [erroneously]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dAy^irap","text_ar":"دايِرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaf~","text_ar":"كَفّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the back-toe:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) so says IDrd. (O.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramolapN EajozaA='u","text_ar":"رَمْلَةٌ عَجْزَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A high piece of sand:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an oblong piece of sand producing plants"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a high oblong piece of sand, as though it were hard ground, not sand heaped up, but fertile:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EujozN","text_ar":"عُجْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", because it is an epithet. (T, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA","M"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}